[?2004l[?2004h> - resp_dat: 1750 images (rows) x 20 voxels (columns) - brain responses to training images
[?2004l[?2004h> - val_feat: 120 images (rows) x 10921 features (columns) - validation images for prediction
[?2004l[?2004h> - loc_dat: 20 voxels (rows) x 3 (columns) - spatial location of the voxels
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> Requirements:
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 1. Install R if not already available, then implement your solution in R
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 2. Data Partitioning:
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Split the training data (fit_feat, resp_dat) into three sets:
[?2004l[?2004h>      * Training set: 50% of the data
[?2004l[?2004h>      * Validation set: 25% of the data  
[?2004l[?2004h>      * Test set: 25% of the data
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Use seed 42 for reproducibility
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 3. Model Implementation:
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Implement LASSO regression with the following model selection criteria:
